description: Galen really stands out in a crowd. He is tall, handsome and has a nicely toned body. He swims, plays basketball and works out 7 days a week, and it shows - he's fit as fuck! Interesting fact: He is divorced, single and ready to mingle. This self-proclaimed goofball is always looking for new ways to spice up his sex life by introducing new things and new partners every week. This stud is insatiable!
title: Galen
